2. Create a module to perform string operations
File: string_operations.py
def upper_case(s):
    return s.upper()

def lower_case(s):
    return s.lower()

def reverse(s):
    return s[::-1]
File: main.py
import string_operations

text = input("Enter a string: ")

print(string_operations.upper_case(text))
print(string_operations.lower_case(text))
print(string_operations.reverse(text))

